			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A\r\n- Go to the Murder Tribunal (goto -1284 1 504) (near S_LOW_MurderTribunal_Sarevok_ae9f784a-ea64-4297-95a7-8377e85231b6)\r\n- If you want to do the trial, check LOW_MurderTribunal_Sarevok_Trial for further instructions.\r\n- If you want to skip ahead, use ReCon command \"oe MT_Baptism\" or \"MT_Baptism_Dead\" (for Valeria to have already been killed)."
				},
